      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Client infomation -->
<div class="landing-client" id="client">
  <div class="wrapper-client-info">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="client-info">
        <div class="client-info-left">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0px;">Find the right the developer for the right job.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="client-info-right">
          <p>In need for a developer? On our platform, we offer a broad range of developers with different skills. Peek around in their portfolio or post your job offer and find a perfect match!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr style="border-top: solid 2px rgb(48,43,44); width: 40em;">

      <div class="client-images">
        <div class="image-description">
          <div class="description-left">
            <h3>You have an idea!</h3>
            <p>First ask yourself the following questions. Is your idea something where programming skills are required? Do you not know how to transform it into a product? </p>
          </div>

          <div class="description-right">
            <%= image_tag 'idea.png'  %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="client-images">
        <div class="image-description">
          <div class="description-left">
            <%= image_tag 'no-clue.png'  %>
          </div>

          <div class="description-right">
            <h3>Where to start?</h3>
            <p>Define what kind of developer you need. What kind of programming languages do you want him to speak? Do you need a front-end, back-end or full-stack developer? Do you need him or her to have additional skills? When you know what you want, you increase the change on a succesfull match.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="client-images">
        <div class="image-description">
          <div class="description-left">
            <h3>TJENGA!</h3>
            <p>
            We love to create perfect matches. Please let us know if you find a great developer. We love to hear success stories created on our platform. Also, we aim to improve the platform all the time. If you have any suggestions for improvement, feedback or other shout-outs, please let us know
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="description-right">
            <%= image_tag 'find-tjenga.png'  %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="client-images">
        <div class="image-description">
          <div class="description-left">
            <%= image_tag 'love-tjenga.png'  %>
          </div>

          <div class="description-right">
            <h3>Post your job!</h3>
            <p> At Tjenga, it is also possible to post a job offer. Developers can see your job offer and apply. This way you can find even more fitting developers!! Lets start as soon as you can!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

